    "heading_text": "Response Status Code",
    "anchor_id": "response-status-code",
    "section_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/path-operation-configuration/#response-status-code",
    "section_text": "You can define the (HTTP) status_code to be used in the response of your path operation .\n\nYou can pass directly the int code, like 404 .\n\nBut if you don't remember what each number code is for, you can use the shortcut constants in status :\n\nThat status code will be used in the response and will be added to the OpenAPI schema.",
